{"tid":2208003,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"7月僅准145個簽證！ 中国學生獲美簽「雪崩式下跌」","createTime":"2020-09-18T14:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T07:23:23.000Z","uid":58841,"like":48,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"05b94e3a5c3e004c139ac22809ecf149e5208fb3","tid":2208003,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:14:09.000Z","msg":"〔編譯孫宇青／綜合報導〕美中關係持續緊張之際，美國國務院數據顯示，今年7月對中國（不含香港）公民僅發放百餘個學生簽證，與去年同期的2萬多個相差甚遠。儘管武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）是「雪崩式」下跌的主因，但業內人士坦言，還有其他影響因素。<br />\n<br />\n《自由亞洲電台》（RFA）14日報導，美國國務院領事事務局數據顯示，今年7月共批准145個中國公民的學生簽證（F-1 visa），其中4個由美國駐北京大使館、駐上海總領事館、駐廣州總領事館發出，另141個可能是續簽。相較之下，美國駐香港和台灣的外交機構共批准近千個學生簽證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3292476\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3292476&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCt8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=7b2da957\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3292476&h=67abd248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3292476</a><br />\n<br />\n舊年6月批左3萬幾個簽證俾支那仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-bde070a2624b1448e69c8521368b6a0b_720w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic4.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-bde070a2624b1448e69c8521368b6a0b_720w.jpg&h=db896cb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年6月得8個<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-bde070a2624b1448e69c8521368b6a0b_720w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic4.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-bde070a2624b1448e69c8521368b6a0b_720w.jpg&h=db896cb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aac01bcd53be3abaf36a0f064cd0996a6646f3a6","tid":2208003,"uid":58841,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:14:48.000Z","msg":"仆街貼錯圖<br />\n舊年6月<img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-7aef767dd349d8cea3094a228fc5bd0c_720w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-7aef767dd349d8cea3094a228fc5bd0c_720w.jpg&h=78660db1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4ca7379d216913142c8a22708dc78161480280f","tid":2208003,"uid":171273,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:15:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0049090a114bad1f25f6cc096c5b4b9a8eba96b","tid":2208003,"uid":218731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:15:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e5a8553b9f82b3c014481efa501b1391745528","tid":2208003,"uid":160373,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:16:09.000Z","msg":"難保果145個都係間碟<br />\ndistrust and verify"},{"pid":"cacafe838f13f5131d7d3efc846310f3605a73a0","tid":2208003,"uid":58841,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:16:41.000Z","msg":"唔批支那仔簽證短期內睇唔到效果<br />\n長遠黎睇過多五年左右支那就會無哂浸過鹹水既人材<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d910294981830f557714d322afb50f56d128d64b","tid":2208003,"uid":55571,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:16:52.000Z","msg":"雪崩我聽落以為跌咗8,9 成<br />\n點知1%都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a002c977eb77b003925d994dec58bb855eafcb1","tid":2208003,"uid":58841,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"d910294981830f557714d322afb50f56d128d64b","tid":2208003,"uid":55571,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:16:52.000Z","msg":"雪崩我聽落以為跌咗8,9 成<br />\n點知1%都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:17:44.000Z","msg":"舊年7月批左2萬1個<br />\n係崩左99.3%<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a9744221fe245a5427573097cd71173708ccdf","tid":2208003,"uid":276525,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:18:06.000Z","msg":"關唔關美國嗰邊肺炎事？會唔會申請都少咗？6月好似未正式反間諜"},{"pid":"3f0b862ffae5